'''Adrienne Marie Wilkinson''' is an [[Wikipedia:American|American]] actress of Irish, Scottish, English, Cherokee, Danish, and German heritage.

==Biography==
Wilkinson provided the likeness, expressions and voice of [[Maris Brood]] in ''[[Star Wars: The Force Unleashed]]'' as well as in the [[Wikipedia:Wii|Nintendo Wii]] version of ''[[Star Wars: The Force Unleashed II]]'', as well as the voices of several ambient characters in ''[[Star Wars: The Old Republic]]'', and the [[Daughter]] in ''[[Star Wars: The Clone Wars]]''. She appeared at [[Celebration IV]] for the [[Hyperspace: The Official Star Wars Fan Club|Fan Club]] "Meet & Greet" session from 3:00–4:00 PM on [[May 28]], [[2007]].

